#Internal strings need to use "" instead of '' to match up with the data write functions, so external string markers should always be '' and internal always "". But note that you cannot have a third level at all because of the interpreter reading the internal ' as the closing quote for the initial ' (ex: 'First Level "Second Level 'ThirdLevel'"').
